data.description: PRICE REDUCED!  Great value for this fantastic 3 BR/2.5 BA POOL HOME with fenced back yard, in the heart of Melbourne! Newer roof, newer kitchen appliances and a lovely open Great Room floor plan!  Formal dining room, kitchen with views of the pool and also a sunny breakfast nook!  Ceilings are vaulted in the Great Room which makes this large room even more spacious.  French doors in Great Room lead to your screened lanai area and pool - perfect for your family or entertaining!  Bedrooms are large as well and primary bedroom has sliding doors to the lanai and pool too! This home has been lovingly cared for by its owners. Priced to sell!
